{"type":"message","id":"76c0f6c0","parentId":"001604bb","timestamp":"2026-06-06T20:03:27.209Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:033adb0b-f08b-47e9-a0f6-a71bfe729a9d 每日 skill 升级检查] 执行每日 skill 升级检查。\n\n1. 运行 `clawhub list` 查看当前已装的 skill\n2. 运行 `clawhub update --all --no-input --force` 升级所有 skill\n3. 如果有 skill 升级失败，记下错误信息\n4. 汇报格式：\n   - 检查时间（Asia/Shanghai）\n   - 升级成功的 skill（列出版本号变化）\n   - 升级失败的 skill（列出错误）\n   - 已是最新、没动的 skill（仅列数量）\n5. 如果所有 skill 都已是最新，回复一句话即可，不要冗长\n\n注意：\n- 不要主动修改配置文件\n- 任何破坏性操作前先 stop 并汇报\nCurrent time: Sunday, June 7th, 2026 - 04:03 (Asia/Shanghai)\nReference UTC: 2026-06-06 20:03 UTC\n\nUse the message tool if you need to notify the user directly for the current chat. If you do not send directly, your final plain-text reply will be delivered automatically."}],"timestamp":1780776207207}}
{"type":"message","id":"c70c6988","parentId":"76c0f6c0","timestamp":"2026-06-06T20:03:32.201Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to execute a daily skill upgrade check. Let me follow the instructions:\n\n1. Run `clawhub list` to see currently installed skills\n2. Run `clawhub update --all --no-input --force` to upgrade all skills\n3. Record any failures\n4. Report in the specified format\n\nLet me start by reading the clawhub skill to understand the proper commands, then execute them.\n\nActually, let me just run the commands directly. The user has given me specific commands to run.\n\nLet me start by listing the current skills, then upgrading them.","thinkingSignature":"24c33231b125d1b29c288bc4e18f9e118e68acac5fc250d80517af01a4b78511"},{"type":"text","text":"I'll execute the daily skill upgrade check now."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vfobm320cm74_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub list 2>&1","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":197,"output":170,"cacheRead":49906,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50273,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780776207228,"responseId":"0673b00f67bb28b3e3338b9ee9d5247a"}}
